===Etymology===
右 is from the combination of the phonetic element [[又]], semantically a [[protecting]] [[right]] [[arm]], and [[口]], which here merely signifies an [[object]]. The [[right]] [[hand]] is traditionally the one used in [[protecting]] an [[object]] while carrying it.

